In summary, current researches lack a highly accurate LIBs capacity fade model that effectively couples multiple fading factors across extended cycling periods and a wide-temperature range. Table 4
                         provides a detailed comparison between the model developed in this study and existing relevant models. The results confirm the superiority of the proposed method over prior studies, as it accounts for more factors, delivers higher accuracy, and operates across a wider-temperature range (Fig. 7
                        ).
